3 FOR the purpose of providing that authorizing the Maryland Small Business Development
4 Financing Authority to authorize the provision of a guaranty under the Small
5 Business Guaranty Fund may be supported by the full faith and credit of the State
6 of Maryland or approved in a certain other manner; and generally relating to the
7 Small Business Guaranty Fund.
